---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing — Blog"
  description="The oriz blog is free to read. No paywall, no subscription required."
  hideSidebar={true}
>
  <header class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">Blog</a> / Pricing</p>
    <h1>Pricing</h1>
  </header>

  <article class="prose">
    <p class="lede">
      Reading the oriz blog is free. There is no paywall, no subscription,
      and no premium tier.
    </p>

    <h2>What's free</h2>
    <p>
      All posts, all archives, all feeds (RSS, Atom, JSON). The newsletter
      (when it launches) will be free at no charge. The full content is open
      source under the repo's chosen license.
    </p>

    <h2>How this is sustainable</h2>
    <p>
      The blog runs on free-tier infrastructure (Cloudflare Pages) and the
      author writes for the long-tail benefit of the oriz family of sites,
      not for ad revenue. If you want to support the work, the best thing
      you can do is share a post with one other person.
    </p>

    <p>
      Questions: <a href="/contact/">contact</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
